Class NumberValue

java.lang.Object
  org.multigraph.datatypes.DataValue
      org.multigraph.datatypes.number.NumberValue

public class NumberValue
extends DataValue

NumberValue is the DataValue implementation for the NUMBER DataType. It represents a numerical data value. The value is stored internally as a double.
